d, \u201cVerily, Allah will not let my nation agree upon misguidance. The hand of Allah is over the united community.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The interpretation of the united community, according to the scholars, are the people of Fiqh,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/13\/deen-naseehah\/","url_meta":{"origin":39937,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nasihah: Islam is goodwill to Allah and the people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said three times, \u201cThe religion is sincere goodwill.\u201d They said, \u201cTo whom?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo Allah, to His Book, to the leaders of the Muslims and their common people.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1926 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1918,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/02\/treated-as-you-treat-others\/","url_meta":{"origin":39937,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Justice: Allah treats you as you treat others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sirmah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever harms others, Allah will harm him. Whoever is harsh with others, Allah will be harsh with him.\u201d So